---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 338
      - text: "你变强了……真的变强了呢。\n米法的祈福也一定能更多地帮助到你。"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 332
      - text: "现在的你一定可以拯救这个海拉鲁……\n还有在城堡里……等待着你的公主……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 258
      - text: "……你果然好厉害。\n我那时候连还手的余地都没有就被它打倒了……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 298
      - text: "林可，你现在肯定不会输给盖侬了。\n我的祈福也会助你一臂之力的……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk120:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 184
      - text: 所以……请救救那个人吧……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 185
      - text: 如果你去卓拉领地的话，请替我告诉他们……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 129
      - text: 替我向我父亲说一声“对不起”……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 125
      - text: 替我向希多说一声“加油”……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 256
      - text: "……以及，今后替我向公主说一声\n“我还想和你一起谈论更多的事情”……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk240:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 191
      - text: "还有……\n不，没什么了……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 176
      - text: "……林可，\n如果……今后你在别处……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 153
      - text: 找到了我的日记……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 125
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 100
      - text: 你一定不能看啊。
      - control:
          kind: text_size
          percent: 100
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk330:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 224
      - text: "啊……对不起，我不该这么大声的……\n不过……求你了……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 204
      - text: "……林可，你还记得我们一起\n击退怪物时的事情吗？"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 269
      - text: "当领地里的民众因栖息在雷兽山上的莱尼尔\n而惶惶不安时，是你来到了我们身边……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 112
      - text: 随后我们两人便开始了并肩战斗……
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 115
      - text: 这些事……你都忘记了吗？
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 238
      - text: "对了，林可……关于100年前领地里的\n那些回忆，你还记得多少？"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 259
      - text: "卓拉铠甲穿在你身上为何会如此合身，\n你该不会忘记了吧……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 309
      - text: "虽然我希望你能把所有的事情都回忆起来，\n但实在想不起来的话，那也没办法……"
  Npc_Zora_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 182
      - text: 不过……我会永远记得这些事情……
